- if page.parent.status.nil?
  - page.parent.status = 'red'
%div{ class: "status-#{page.parent.status}"}
  %p
    | This site is currently under development, and may contain inaccurate and misleading information. 
    %a.button(href="https://issues.jboss.org/secure/CreateIssue!default.jspa" target="_blank") Report an issue 
    %br
    | Status: #{page.parent.status.capitalize}. Known issues: 

    - unless page.parent.issues.nil?
      - for issue in page.parent.issues
        %a(href='https://issues.jboss.org/browse/#{issue}')
        | #{issue}
    - else 
      | None


